sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as 浏览器用户
  participant FE as 前端页面
  participant API as Flask API
  participant DB as MySQL
  participant COL as 采集器
  participant NOTI as 通知通道

  U->>FE: 输入品类/目标价/方向
  FE->>API: GET /api/price-alert/subscribe?data_type=...&target=...&op=...
  API-->>FE: event: ping
  loop 周期推送
    COL->>DB: 写入最新价格
    API->>DB: 读取最新价
    API-->>FE: event: price (当前价)
    alt 满足触发条件
      API-->>FE: event: alert (触发价/时间/原因)
      opt 配置多通道
        API->>NOTI: 发送通知(企业微信/Telegram/邮件)
      end
    end
  end

